    <section class="intro">
        <h2>About Euphoria Check</h2>
        <p>Euphoria Check is an open-source web application designed to assess your well-being and happiness based on the PERMA model developed by psychologist Martin Seligman.</p>
        <p>Answer a series of questions and receive a personalized PERMA score, along with insights and a goal-setting email to help you on your journey to greater happiness.</p>
    </section>

